{
  "texts": [
    "Then, 3D-DenseNets with various designs were combined using a weighted-based fusion technique.",
    "By altering the hyperparameter initializations and architecture, a base 3D-DenseNet was built.",
    "A weighted-based fusion technique was employed to integrate the basis classifiers.",
    "Accuracy was gradually increased using the ensemble model instead of merely taking the network's forecast average.",
    "In Chitradevi and Prabha (2020), the authors divided the brain into smaller sections, including the gray matter, white matter, and hippocampus, using various optimization methods, including the Cuckoo Search, Gray Wolf Optimization, Particle Swarm Optimization, and Genetic Algorithm."
  ]
}